"2452","(1) On February 28, 2018, the Board of Trustees of Wells Fargo Funds Trust"
"2453","approved a reduction to the investment management fee and name change of the"
"2454","Small Cap Opportunities Fund to the Disciplined Small Cap Fund. Subject to"
"2455","shareholder approval of the new Wells Capital Management sub-advisory"
"2456","agreement, the name change and following fee schedule will become effective"
"2457","on or about June 15, 2018: First 1B 0.50; Next 4B 0.475; Next 5B 0.44;"
"2458","Over 10B 0.43"
"2459","Schedule A amended: February 28, 2018"
"2460","(+) As long as the Fund invests all (or substantially all) of its assets in a"
"2461","single, registered, open-end management investment company in accordance with"
"2462","Section 12(d)(1)(E) under the 1940 Act, the Fund pays Funds Management an"
"2463","investment management fee for the Fund-level administrative services set forth"
"2464","in Section 2(b) of the Investment Management Agreement.  At the time the Fund"
"2465","invests some of its assets in two or more registered, open-end management"
"2466","investment companies in accordance with Section 12(d)(1)(G) under the 1940 Act,"
"2467","the Fund shall pay Funds Management an investment management fee for combined"
"2468","asset allocation services and fund-level administrative services at the rates"
"2469","shown in the table that follows."
"2470","     Dormant Investment Management Fee"
"2471","     as % of Avg. Daily Net Asset Value"
"2472","       First 5B      0.30"
"2473","       Next 5B       0.29"
"2474","       Over 10B      0.28"
"2475","The foregoing fee schedule is agreed to as of February 28, 2018 and shall"
"2476","remain in effect until changed in writing by the parties."
