"2740","Section 4. Delegation of Responsibilities. The Manager"
"2741","may carry out any of its obligations under this Agreement (other"
"2742","than under Section 2(b) hereof) by employing, subject to"
"2743","supervision by the Manager, one or more Sub-Manager(s) who are"
"2744","registered as investment advisers pursuant to the Investment"
"2745","Advisers Act of 1940 (Sub-Advisers). Each Sub-Adviser's"
"2746","employment will be evidenced by a separate written agreement"
"2747","approved by the Board and if required, receiving any other"
"2748","approvals required under the 1940 Act(unless the Commission or"
"2749","its staff has given authorization or issued an interpretation"
"2750","dispensing with any such requirement). The Manager shall not be"
"2751","liable hereunder for any act or omission of any Sub-Adviser,"
"2752","except for failure to exercise good faith in the employment of the"
"2753","Sub-Adviser and for failure to exercise appropriate supervision of"
"2754","such Sub-Adviser, and as may otherwise be agreed in writing. The"
"2755","Manager shall be solely responsible for compensating any Sub-"
"2756","Adviser for services rendered under any Sub-Advisory Agreement."
"2757","The Manager may, from time to time and at any time, terminate"
"2758","any Sub-Adviser and reassume the responsibilities assigned to such"
"2759","Sub-Adviser with respect to any Fund solely with the approval of"
"2760","the Board."
"2761","Section 5. Control by Board. Any investment"
"2762","management activities undertaken by the Manager pursuant to this"
"2763","Agreement, as well as any other activities undertaken by the"
"2764","Manager on behalf of the Funds, shall at all times be subject to the"
"2765","direction and control of the Board."
