"3042","Section 21. Wells Fargo Name. The Manager and the"
"3043","Trust each agree that the name Wells Fargo, which comprises a"
"3044","component of the Trust's name, is a property right of the parent of"
"3045","the Manager. The Trust agrees and consents that: (i) it will use the"
"3046","words Wells Fargo as a component of its corporate name, the"
"3047","name of any series or class, or all of the above, and for no other"
"3048","purpose; (ii) it will not grant to any third party the right to use the"
"3049","name Wells Fargo for any purpose; (iii) the Manager or any"
"3050","corporate affiliate of the Manager may use or grant to others the"
"3051","right to use the words Wells Fargo, or any combination or"
"3052","abbreviation thereof, as all or a portion of a corporate or business"
"3053","name or for any commercial purpose, other than a grant of such"
"3054","right to another registered investment company not advised by the"
"3055","Manager or one of its affiliates; and (iv) in the event that the"
"3056","Manager or an affiliate thereof is no longer acting as investment"
"3057","adviser to any Fund, the Trust shall, upon request by the Manager,"
"3058","promptly take such action as may be necessary to change its"
"3059","corporate name to one not containing the words Wells Fargo and"
"3060","following such change, shall not use the words Wells Fargo, or"
"3061","any combination thereof, as a part of its corporate name or for any"
"3062","other commercial purpose, and shall use its best efforts to cause its"
"3063","trustees, officers and other relevant parties to take any and all"
"3064","actions that the Manager may request to effect the foregoing and to"
"3065","reconvey to the Manager any and all rights to such words."
"3066","Section 22. Risk Acknowledgement. The Manager does"
"3067","not guarantee the future performance of the Funds or any specific"
"3068","level of performance, the success of any investment decision or"
"3069","strategy that the Manager may use, or the success of the Manager's"
"3070","overall management of the Funds. The Trust understands that"
"3071","investment decisions made for the Funds by the Manager are"
"3072","subject to various market, currency, economic and business risks,"
"3073","and that those investment decisions will not always be profitable."
"3074","The Manager will manage only the securities, cash and other"
"3075","investments for which management responsibility is delegated to it"
"3076","and which are held in the Funds' account(s) and, in making"
"3077","investment decisions for the Funds, the Manager will not consider"
"3078","any other securities, cash or other investments owned by the Trust."
"3079","Section 23. No Third Party Beneficiaries. Nothing in this"
"3080","Agreement shall be deemed to confer on any person other than the"
"3081","parties hereto any benefits, rights, remedies, obligations or"
"3082","liabilities under or by reason of this Agreement. No person shall"
"3083","be deemed to be a third-party beneficiary of this Agreement."
"3084","IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the parties hereto have caused this Agreement"
"3085","to be executed in duplicate by their respective officers on the"
"3086","day and year first written above."
